{"tid":162881,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無可能幫自己製造假死亡證據","createTime":"2017-03-19T14:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T05:50:25.000Z","uid":79711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c03fe8865a8a9225090fb4d5e2f736d73ffd8106","tid":162881,"uid":79711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:43:51.000Z","msg":"幫自己製造死亡證據<br />\n係現實呢個身份已經死亡<br />\n身邊既人，屋企人，同學朋友都以為自己過左身 <br />\n係法律上已判定死亡同埋唔存在<br />\n呢個世界再無人認識你 <br />\n好似second life咁樣<br />\n係另一個國家/地方生活，打咩工/做咩都無咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生活係香港 做人辛苦 生活更辛苦<br />\n成日睇戲好似好易有門路做到假護照假身份，俾唔知一兩萬鎊就有第三世界護照<br />\n現實中其實有無可能造到假身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：生活壓力大 純FF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a9f303665d29caf2c0a1e4bd068ddfb002eaa5","tid":162881,"uid":79711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:45:18.000Z","msg":"要證實死亡都要有條屍<br />\n<br />\n有無方法意外係幫到自己做到死亡證據呢？<br />\n<br />\n失蹤就唔計啦"},{"pid":"c943418cdacb67d3e8b6e0a0418e59c9e4a611a7","tid":162881,"uid":77697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:52:17.000Z","msg":"留名想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最唔捨得係我阿婆"},{"pid":"204cba257c7a0897446f851e1c095fc9fadee2ad","tid":162881,"uid":15339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:52:23.000Z","msg":"又係你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deae5f36db4b3543785cab21e2ad5aba5df68c57","tid":162881,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要證實死亡都要有條屍<br />\n<br />\n有無方法意外係幫到自己做到死亡證據呢？<br />\n<br />\n失蹤就唔計啦</blockquote><br />\n馬斯丹上校"},{"pid":"f82ef10e9204d4548137df7f0ec896d6f8d34c76","tid":162881,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:30:17.000Z","msg":"你唔死都可以去第三世界生